data.description: **SELLER OFFERING 5K IN CLOSING COST CREDITS!!** Come see this charming 2 bedroom/2 bath bungalow in an upcoming Cleveland neighborhood! This home has been beautifully updated head to toe within the past two years! The kitchen features white shaker cabinets, a lovely subway-tile backsplash and stainless steel appliances! The update also features new flooring, paint and fixtures throughout. And you can rest easy knowing the major items were not left out of the renovation; HVAC, roof, plumbing and wiring were all taken care as well! The home showcases the original fireplace though now it is for show or vent-less gas logs now. The layout is great for families, students or those looking to ''house-hack'' with one bedroom and one bath on each level allowing for maximum privacy. You won't want to miss this one, so schedule your showings today!
